			"text": "The user can pop the stash as long as:\n1. They aren't ACTIVELY syncing (they should STOP instead)\n2. Git & untracked file state is clean\n# TODO: handle user-mangled stash edge cases. May be annoying",
			"rawText": "The user can pop the stash as long as:\n1. They aren't ACTIVELY syncing (they should STOP instead)\n2. Git & untracked file state is clean\n# TODO: handle user-mangled stash edge cases. May be annoying",
